Data disclaimer
---------------
ALL data in `pretense_compliance_standards/` is SYNTHETIC and fake by construction
(reserved/never-issued identifier ranges, example.com emails, test-mode secret
prefixes, Luhn-valid-but-random card numbers). Every corpus file carries a
"SYNTHETIC — FAKE COMPLIANCE TEST DATA, NOT REAL" banner. No value maps to a real
person, account, or secret. It is scanner test input for measuring detection
coverage — never real regulated data.
